title: Maokai's S6 skin
body: > Who knows why I did not get Maokai's S6 skin. My rank level is Gold IV. I did not have Maokai champion, and I got it free today but I did not get the skin. Who knows that's why????

replies.body: Thanks Zombiemaster!  Aye, hang tight as the rewards aren't completely done just yet.  A lot of players have received their rewards, but still missing some content like the victorious skin.  Hang tight, it's coming!

> [{quoted}](name=Porocles,realm=NA,application-id=osqw6G4M,discussion-id=O8qOZk6k,comment-id=0000,timestamp=2016-11-10T19:01:44.693+0000)
>
> You may see that some content is still missing or that one player may have received them sooner than another, but don't worry!  Per the [Season 6 FAQ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2016-ranked-season-ends-soon), we aim to have this wrapped up by the 21st.  Hope that helps offer some ease!
